      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable daily driver. While it runs well and has been regularly maintained, it shows noticeable signs of its age, including several scratches and minor dings on the exterior paint. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though the cabin remains functional and comfortable. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at an accessible price point.",
