    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. From the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, every detail has been meticulously maintained. If you're looking for a top-tier vehicle that requires zero compromises, this is the one for you!",
