    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a comfortable and confident driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some light signs of use consistent with careful ownership, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. Buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road with no immediate major repairs needed.",
